Package: lpnet
Type: Package
Title: Consruct a circular network based on a tree by Linear Programming
Description: Form a nex file or distance matrix, use tree construction method, Linear Programming(LP), Non-negative least squares(nnls) to construt a circular split network which can be seen in SplitsTree4.
Version: 0.1.0
